		<div class="limit">
		
			
					<h2 style="text-align: center;">&#8220;<span style="color: #cc99ff;">A spectacular night of</span> first class entertainment.&#8221;</h2>
<div>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;"><strong>Scotia</strong></span> are one of Scotland&#8217;s most sought after ceilidh bands. From complete beginners to the most experienced ceilidh dancers, we cater for every kind of audience and with our fantastically entertaining MC we guarantee to have everyone up on their feet.</p>
<hr />
<p><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yZeoJ4CuEjk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe><br />
&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-300 size-full" src="http://scotiaceilidh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/240.jpg" alt="" width="240" height="240" srcset="http://scotiaceilidh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/240.jpg 240w, http://scotiaceilidh.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/240-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px" /></strong></p>
<h2><strong>&#8220;A PROPER Ceilidh&#8221;</strong> <span style="color: #cc99ff;">&#8211; The Best of Scottish Music</span></h2>
<p>Our award-winning musicians will provide a night filled with a fantastic range of traditional &amp; contemporary Scottish music &#8211; as well as some classics that will have everyone singing along.</p>
<p>The band most regularly performs as a 3 piece with <strong><span style="color: #cc99ff;">accordion</span></strong>, <strong><span style="color: #cc99ff;">fiddle</span></strong> and <span style="color: #cc99ff;"><strong>drums</strong></span> but can extend to a 4 or 5 piece for larger events. Combining your night with a <span style="color: #cc99ff;"><a style="color: #cc99ff;" title="Disco" href="http://scotiaceilidh.com/disco/"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Scotia Disco</span></strong></span></a></span> provides the perfect mix for your guests and will have the dancefloor filled with songs spanning several decades.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">
</div>
							
